description: This header file defines the interface for the exported API functions of the Dslh Object Record (Obj Record) component, including creation, removal, enrollment, and initialization functions.

methods.name: DslhCreateObjRecord
methods.description: Creates a new object record with specified container, owner, and reserved contexts.

methods.name: DslhObjroCreate
methods.description: Creates an instance of the object record.

methods.name: DslhObjroRemove
methods.description: Removes and deallocates the object record instance.

methods.name: DslhObjroEnrollObjects
methods.description: Enrolls necessary objects into the object record.

methods.name: DslhObjroInitialize
methods.description: Initializes the object record with default and setup parameters.
